#. <section class="sutta" id="sn37.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Tīhidhammehisutta → tīhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Tīhidhammehisutta"
msgstr "4. Three Qualities"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.240"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo yebhuyyena kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when females have three qualities females, when their body "
"breaks up, after death, they are mostly reborn in a place of loss, a bad "
"place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, mātugāmo pubbaṇhasamayaṃ maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā "
"agāraṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""
"A female lives at home with a heart full of the stain of stinginess in the "
"morning, envy in the afternoon, and sexual desire in the evening."

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.4"
msgid "Majjhanhikasamayaṃ issāpariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.5"
msgid "Sāyanhasamayaṃ kāmarāgapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn37.4:1.6"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo yebhuyyena kāyassa "
"bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When females have these three qualities, when their body breaks up, after "
"death, they are mostly reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the "
"underworld, hell.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.4:1.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

